query:
SELECT 
  ce.id,
  c.name as course_name,
  ce.trainee_count,
  ce.paid_amount,
  ce.enrollment_date
FROM course_enrollments ce
LEFT JOIN courses c ON ce.course_id = c.id
WHERE ce.enrollment_date >= '2025-02-01' AND ce.enrollment_date <= '2025-02-28'
ORDER BY ce.enrollment_date;
